WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
Your diabetes info shouldn't be scattered everywhere.

00:06.000 --> 00:17.000
One lab result in an email. One prescription in a pharmacy app. One note in a portal. One receipt in a text. One question you meant to ask — gone. That's the problem.

00:17.000 --> 00:24.000
Diabetes creates a lot of little pieces. And when life gets busy, those pieces get lost.

00:24.000 --> 00:32.000
The win is simple. A private diabetes vault.

00:32.000 --> 00:43.000
Your A1C history, medication list, foot-care notes, insurance cards, supply orders, doctor questions, emergency contacts. All in one place.

00:43.000 --> 00:51.000
Close to you. Owned by you. Ready when you need it.

00:51.000 --> 00:59.000
Diabetes is a 24/7 job. You don't have to carry it alone.

00:59.000 --> 01:06.000
LocalDiabetic. We just help you carry the day. Win big.
